<br>
I tried to say it was camped for a while, but people kept taking all my mobs, named or not.  I am not going to run around the temple and snatch a named from the opposite side I am sitting if a group is there.  Nor am I going to dispell other peoples pulls if they do that to me.  Ignore the jerks in the zone, talk to the people around you.  Most of the time I can work out a system with people in the zone.  Where they take the back and I take the front etc.<br>
<br>
Saying the zone is FFA is an excuse to act like an @#%$ in many cases.  We will never get everyone to agree on a system here.  Let us just leave it like this.  Treat others like you want them to treat you.<br>
<br>
Valkyry<br>
Level 60 Wizard<br>
